  txtCauHoi:
  - A tailor has a sheet of fabric that is 10 meters long. Every day he cuts a piece
    2 meters long. So after how many days will he cut all that fabric?
  - "M\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi th\u1EE3 may c\xF3 m\u1ED9t t\u1EA5m v\u1EA3i d\xE0i
    10m. M\u1ED7i ng\xE0y anh c\u1EAFt m\u1ED9t \u0111o\u1EA1n d\xE0i 2m. V\u1EADy
    sau bao nhi\xEAu ng\xE0y ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\xF3 s\u1EBD c\u1EAFt h\u1EBFt
    s\u1ED1 v\u1EA3i \u0111\xF3?"
  hienThiVanBanGiaiThich: 1
  txtGiaiThich:
  - When cutting on the 4th day, that piece of fabric is only 2 meters so there is
    no need to cut anymore
  - "Khi c\u1EAFt v\xE0o ng\xE0y th\u1EE9 4, m\u1EA3nh v\u1EA3i \u0111\xF3 ch\u1EC9
